			<div class="LayoutContainer" style="display:block;" ><div><div style="display:block;overflow:hidden;" ><ul style="font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;">
    <li><b style="color: #000000; font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; line-height: normal;">If you are an </b><b style="color: #000000; font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"><i>attorney</i></b><span style="color: #000000; font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"><b style="font-style: normal;"> seeking information on Dr. Neppe's medico-legal forensics services, </b><a href="forensic.php#Medico_Legal_Forensics_Contact_Form" style="font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">click here</a></span></li>
</ul>
<ul style="font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;">
    <li><span style="color: #000000; font-family: verdana, geneva, kalimati, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">
    <i>Please note that Dr. Neppe does not consult with individuals who may be in litigation.&nbsp; If the client contacts Dr.Neppe directly, it may lead to him not taking the case.</i></span></li>
